1. e4 c5 2. Nf3 d6 3. d4 cxd4 4. Qxd4 a6 {This move is also intended to stop
White from playing Bb5 after Black's Nc6. However, our idea is to play Qe3 in
response to Nc6 anyway and therefore this move is just a loss of tempo for
Black. We proceed with our typical plan of playing Be2, Qe3, c4, etc} (4... Nd7
5. c4 Ngf6 6. Nc3 a6 7. Be2 e6 8. O-O Qc7 9. Rd1 Be7 10. b3 O-O 11. Ba3 Ne8 (
11... Qa5 12. Bb2 b6 13. Qe3 Bb7 14. Nd4 $14 {[%cal Ga2a3,Gb3b4]}) 12. Qe3 h6
13. e5 Nxe5 14. Nxe5 dxe5 15. Bxe7 Qxe7 16. Qxe5 $16 {[%csl Gd1][%cal Ge2f3,
Gf3a8,Gd1d8] 1-0 (32) Vallejo Pons,F (2707)-Tissir,M (2381) Riyadh KSA 2017}) (
4... e5 {I do not think this move is right especially when both of White's
bishops are not developed yet. Let's say, for example, after 1.e4 c5 2.Nf3 d6
3.d4 cxd4 4.Nxd4 Nf6 5.Nc3 a6 6.Be2 e5 7.Nf3, White moves his bishop again
from e2 to c4 to take control over d5. Or in the 6. Be3 e5 7.Nf3 variation,
White moves his bishop again from e3 to g5 to pin the knight on f6 in order to
capture it at the appropriate moment to take control over the d5-square.
However, in the text position, White can move his bishops to the desired
squares [Bf1-c4 and Bc1-g5] in one move.} 5. Qd1 Nf6 (5... h6 6. Bc4 Nf6 7. Nc3
Be6 (7... Be7 8. O-O a6 9. a4 Qc7 10. Bb3 Nbd7 11. Be3 Nc5 12. Bxc5 Qxc5 13.
Qd3 O-O 14. Nd5 Nxd5 15. Bxd5 Rb8 16. c3 Kh8 17. b4 Qc7 18. a5 $14 {1-0 (58)
Chigaev,M (2550)-Moiseenko,V (2533) St Petersburg RUS 2016}) 8. Bb3 Be7 9. O-O
O-O 10. Be3 Nc6 11. Qe2 Na5 12. Rfd1 Qc7 13. Nd5 Nxd5 14. Bxd5 Nc4 15. c3 $14 {
1/2-1/2 (71) Hou Yifan (2623)-Nakamura,H (2775) Hoogeveen NED 2012}) 6. Bc4 Be7
(6... Nxe4 $2 7. Qd5 $18 {[%cal Rd5f7,Rd5e4]}) 7. Nc3 O-O 8. O-O Be6 (8... h6
9. Qe2 Nc6 10. Rd1 Bg4 11. Be3 Rc8 12. Bb3 a6 13. Nd5 Nxd5 14. Bxd5 Nb4 15. Bb3
$14 {0-1 (63) Petrosian,T (2629)-Zakarian,D (2261) Kallithea GRE 2008}) (8...
Nc6 9. Bg5 Bg4 (9... Be6 10. Bb3 Rc8 (10... a5 11. Bxf6 Bxf6 12. Qd3 {[%csl
Ge4][%cal Gd3e4]} Nb4 13. Qd2 Qb6 14. Rfd1 Be7 15. h3 h6 16. Qe2 Rac8 17. a3 {
[%cal Gc3d5] 1-0 (36) Kolev,A (2569)-Zakarian,D (2344) Kavala 2007}) (10... Ne8
