more active pieces. With his last move Black wants to play b5 to open the
position and stir some active counterplay.} 17. a4 $1 {Black does not have
enough pieces to attack the b3-pawn.} Rac8 {White has now stopped Black's
counterplay and it is now time for him to improve his own pieces:} 18. Rd2 Bf8
19. Rcd1 $14 *

